453
00:28:59,978 --> 00:29:03,514
The tokamak concept
was developed in the 60s,

454
00:29:03,514 --> 00:29:09,946
very soon in the 70s, 
we reached temperatures

455
00:29:09,946 --> 00:29:15,714
of the order of 50 
or even 100 millions of degrees,

