00:30:19,299 --> 00:30:22,292
And that's what we intend to do 
with the ITER project

474
00:30:22,292 --> 00:30:25,731
which aims at obtaining about 10 for Q

475
00:30:25,731 --> 00:30:29,309
and of course for the reactor values 
of capital Q

476
00:30:29,309 --> 00:30:32,786
that are in a range of 30 to 40.

477
00:30:32,786 --> 00:30:37,983
Let's say a few words about ITER
which will be the first burning plasma.

478
00:30:37,983 --> 00:30:41,091
You see here 
the construction site for ITER,

479
00:30:41,091 --> 00:30:45,147
which is located in the south 
of France, Cadarache.

480
00:30:45,147 --> 00:30:47,983
ITER is the result of a very large 
international collaboration

481
00:30:47,983 --> 00:30:54,716
involving several partners representing
